## Quick Start by Module Type

**Testing a GenServer?** Start with: core/start-supervised, otp/test-pure-module-directly, otp/genserver-public-api-only, otp/force-sync-after-cast

**Testing an Ecto schema?** Start with: ecto/changeset-without-db, ecto/constraint-needs-db, ecto/use-errors-on-helper

**Testing a LiveView?** Start with: liveview/test-disconnected-render, liveview/element-scoped-events, liveview/render-async-required

**Testing with Mox?** Start with: mocking/behaviour-before-mock, mocking/mock-at-boundary-only, mocking/verify-on-exit

**Testing an Oban worker?** Start with: oban/perform-job-for-unit, oban/assert-enqueued-for-integration

**Writing property tests?** Start with: property/when-to-use-properties, property/roundtrip-properties
